MAC OSX Build Instructions
--------------------------

To build OpenCPN sucessfully on 10.6 you to install the following tools:

1. Install MacPorts --> http://www.macports.org/
2. Install cmake from MacPorts (port install cmake)
3. Get wxWidgets source -> svn checkout http://svn.wxwidgets.org/svn/wx/wxWidgets/trunk wxWidgets
4. cd into wxWidgets and run ./configure --with-osx-cocoa --disable-std_containers
5. make / make install  (wxWidgets)
6. cd to the opencpn-source dir an run:  mkdir build ; cd build ; cmake .. ; make install
7. run opencpn :  opencpn.app/Contents/MacOS/OpenCPN

